prompt: If you’re concerned about privacy, which of the following pieces of information would you LEAST LIKELY share on a social networking site?
feedback: If you’re concerned about privacy, it means you’re concerned about personal information that shouldn’t be public. A new clothing store isn’t private information. New stores want more people to know about them! A new coffee mug also doesn’t give personal information. A video of a party in a public park is also not very private. The only personal information in the video would be images of people. The best choice is your address. You probably don’t want to give out your address to strangers if you’re concerned about privacy.
